(117, 1689100684, 1686495295, 1688922364, 'Interpola&ccedil;&atilde;o', 'Interpola&ccedil;&atilde;o', '<H1>Interpola&ccedil;&atilde;o</H1>\n\nDado \n$n+1 $\npontos em \n$R^2$\ncom abscissas distintas:\n\n<CENTER>\n$   &#92;underline{p}_i= (x_i,y_i), ~ i=0,&#92;ldots,n$\n</CENTER>\n\nProcuramos um Polin&ocirc;mio de Grau \n$n,$\n interpolando\nestes pontos:\n\n<CENTER>\n$   y_i=P_n(x_i)=a_n x_i^n++a_{n-1}x_i^{n-1}&#92;ldots+a_1 x_1+a_0,&#92;quad i=0,&#92;ldots,n$\n</CENTER>', '2', 98, 1, '1', '', '1', '2', '2', '', '', '/usr/local/Slides/1_Disciplines/1_CN/4_Interpolation', '1', '4_Interpolation', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
