(180, 1689100684, 1686499144, 1686499144, 'Converg&ecirc;ncia', 'Zeros de Fun&ccedil;&otilde;es', '<H2>Converg&ecirc;ncia do Algoritmo da Bisec&ccedil;&atilde;o</H2>\n\n<OL>\n   <LI>\n      3 Sequ&ecirc;ncias: [; a_k &lt; x_k &lt; b_k ;]:\n      <OL TYPE=a>\n         <LI>[; a_{k+1} &#92;geq a_k &#92;wedge a_k &#92;leq b_0  &#92;quad &#92;Leftrightarrow &#92;quad a_k &#92;rightarrow &#92;alpha, &#92;quad k &#92;rightarrow +&#92;infty;]</LI>\n         <LI>[; b_{k+1} &#92;leq b_k &#92;wedge b_k &#92;geq a_0  &#92;quad &#92;Leftrightarrow &#92;quad b_k &#92;rightarrow &#92;beta, &#92;quad k &#92;rightarrow +&#92;infty;]</LI>\n      </OL>\n   </LI>\n   <LI>[; b_k-a_k = &#92;frac{b_0-a_0}{2^k} &#92;rightarrow 0, &#92;quad k &#92;rightarrow +&#92;infty ;]\n   <LI>Teorema do Confronto: \n   [; \n       &#92;lim_{k &#92;rightarrow +&#92;infty} a_k\n       =\n       &#92;lim_{k &#92;rightarrow +&#92;infty} x_k\n       =\n       &#92;lim_{k &#92;rightarrow +&#92;infty} b_k\n       = &#92;xi\n   ;]\n   </LI>\n   <LI>Em cada paso: \n   [;\n      f(a_k) f(b_k) &lt; 0\n      &#92;quad &#92;Leftrightarrow &#92;quad\n      &#92;lim_{k &#92;rightarrow +&#92;infty} f(a_k) f(b_k)&#92;leq 0;]\n    </LI>\n    <LI>[;a_k,b_k;] convergentes:\n       <OL TYPE=a>\n         <LI>\n            [; \n                &#92;lim_{k &#92;rightarrow +&#92;infty} f(a_k) f(b_k)=\n                &#92;lim_{k &#92;rightarrow +&#92;infty} f(a_k) &#92;cdot\n                &#92;lim_{k &#92;rightarrow +&#92;infty} f(b_k)\n           ;]\n            </LI>\n            <LI>[;f;] cont&iacute;nua:\n            <BR>\n            [; \n                &#92;lim_{k &#92;rightarrow +&#92;infty} f(a_k)=\n                f(&#92;lim_{k &#92;rightarrow +&#92;infty} a_k)\n                =\n                f(&#92;xi),\n                &#92;qquad\n                &#92;lim_{k &#92;rightarrow +&#92;infty} f(b_k)=\n                f(&#92;lim_{k &#92;rightarrow +&#92;infty} b_k)\n                =\n                f(&#92;xi)\n           ;]\n        </LI>\n      </OL>\n   </LI>\n   <LI>Ent&atilde;o:\n    [;\n         0 &#92;geq\n         &#92;lim_{k &#92;rightarrow +&#92;infty} f(a_k) f(b_k)\n         =\n         f(&#92;xi)^2 &#92;geq 0\n    ;]\n   </LI>\n   <LI>Novamente, pela Teorema do Confronto: [; f(&#92;xi)=0 ;] &#9643;</LI>\n</OL>', '2', 151, 1, '1', '1', '1', '1', '2', '', '', '/usr/local/Slides/1_Disciplines/1_CN/1_Functions/0_Zeros/1_Bisection/5_Convergencia', '1', '5_Convergencia', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
