(184, 1689100684, 1686499144, 1686499144, 'Atividades #1.1', 'Zeros de Fun&ccedil;&otilde;es', '<H2>Atividades #1.1: Bisec&ccedil;&atilde;o</H2>\n\n<OL>\n   <LI>\n      Crie um arquivo, Functions.py, implementando as seguintes fun&ccedil;&otilde;es:\n      <OL TYPE=a>\n        <LI>\n$          f_1(x)=x^2-1;$\n        </LI>\n        <LI>\n$          f_2(x)=x^4-2x^2-1;$\n        </LI>\n        <LI>\n$          f_3(x)=x^4-4;$\n        </LI>\n        <LI>\n$          f_4(x)=e^x-&#92;frac{1}{2};$\n        </LI>\n        <LI>\n$          f_5(x)=&#92;log{x}+1;$\n        </LI>\n        <LI>\n$          f_6(x)=&#92;cos{x}+&#92;frac{1}{2};$\n        </LI>\n        <LI>\n$          f_7(x)=&#92;sin{x}-&#92;frac{&#92;sqrt{3}}{2};$\n        </LI>\n        <LI>\n$          f_8(x)=&#92;cos{x}-&#92;sin{x};$\n        </LI>\n        <LI>\n$          f_9(x)=e^x-&#92;cos{x};$\n        </LI>\n        <LI>\n$          f_{10}(x)=e^x+&#92;sin{x}.$\n        </LI>\n      </OL>\n      Quais seus dom&iacute;nios e ra&iacute;zes?\n   </LI>\n   <LI>\n     Escolher intervalos adequados e executar o Algoritmo Bisec&ccedil;&atilde;o na fun&ccedil;&otilde;es acima,\n     gerando uma listagem das itera&ccedil;&otilde;es com na sec&ccedil;&atilde;o anterior.\n\n<CENTER><TABLE>\n  <TR>\n     <TD><IMG SRC=\"/cgi-bin/SVG?Curves/Functions/d0R/1_100.svg\" HEIGHT=300px WIDTH=300px></TD>\n     <TD><IMG SRC=\"/cgi-bin/SVG?Curves/Functions/d0R/2_100.svg\" HEIGHT=300px WIDTH=300px></TD>\n  </TR>\n  <TR>\n     <TD><CENTER>\n$          f_1(x)$\n     </CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>\n$          f_2(x)$\n     </CENTER></TD>\n  </TR>\n  <TR>\n     <TD><IMG SRC=\"/cgi-bin/SVG?Curves/Functions/d0R/3_100.svg\" HEIGHT=300px WIDTH=300px></TD>\n     <TD><IMG SRC=\"/cgi-bin/SVG?Curves/Functions/d0R/4_100.svg\" HEIGHT=300px WIDTH=300px></TD>\n  </TR>\n  <TR>\n     <TD><CENTER>\n$          f_3(x)$\n     </CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>\n$          f_4(x)$\n     </CENTER></TD>\n  </TR>\n  <TR>\n     <TD><IMG SRC=\"/cgi-bin/SVG?Curves/Functions/d0R/5_100.svg\" HEIGHT=300px WIDTH=300px></TD>\n     <TD><IMG SRC=\"/cgi-bin/SVG?Curves/Functions/d0R/6_100.svg\" HEIGHT=300px WIDTH=300px></TD>\n  </TR>\n  <TR>\n     <TD><CENTER>\n$          f_5(x)$\n     </CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>\n$          f_6(x)$\n     </CENTER></TD>\n  </TR>\n  <TR>\n     <TD><IMG SRC=\"/cgi-bin/SVG?Curves/Functions/d0R/7_100.svg\" HEIGHT=300px WIDTH=300px></TD>\n     <TD><IMG SRC=\"/cgi-bin/SVG?Curves/Functions/d0R/8_100.svg\" HEIGHT=300px WIDTH=300px></TD>\n  </TR>\n   <TR>\n     <TD><CENTER>\n$          f_7(x)$\n     </CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>\n$          f_8(x)$\n     </CENTER></TD>\n  </TR>\n <TR>\n     <TD><IMG SRC=\"/cgi-bin/SVG?Curves/Functions/d0R/9_100.svg\" HEIGHT=300px WIDTH=300px></TD>\n     <TD><IMG SRC=\"/cgi-bin/SVG?Curves/Functions/d0R/10_100.svg\" HEIGHT=300px WIDTH=300px></TD>\n  </TR>\n  <TR>\n     <TD><CENTER>\n$          f_9(x)$\n     </CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>\n$          f_{10}(x)$\n     </CENTER></TD>\n  </TR>\n</TABLE></CENTER>\n\n   </LI>\n   <LI>\n      Repete a quest&otilde;es anteriores com as fun&ccedil;&otilde;es:\n      <OL TYPE=a>\n        <LI>\n$          f_{11}(x)=x^2+x-6;$\n        </LI>\n        <LI>\n$          f_{12}(x)=x^3-9x+3;$\n        </LI>\n        <LI>\n$          f_{13}(x)=&#92;sqrt{x}-5e^{-x};$\n        </LI>\n        <LI>\n$          f_{14}(x)=x&#92;log{x}-1;$\n        </LI>\n        <LI>\n$          f_{15}(x)=e^{-x^2}-&#92;cos{x};$\n        </LI>\n        <LI>\n$          f_{16}(x)=x^3-x-1;$\n        </LI>\n        <LI>\n$          f_{17}(x)=4 &#92;sin{x}-e^x.$\n        </LI>\n      </OL>\n   </LI>\n</OL>', '2', 151, 1, '1', '1', '1', '2', '2', '', '', '/usr/local/Slides/1_Disciplines/1_CN/1_Functions/0_Zeros/1_Bisection/9_Activities', '1', '9_Activities', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
