(190, 1689100684, 1686499144, 1686499144, 'Atividades 1.4:', 'Atibvidades 1.4:', '<H2>Atividade #1.4-01:</H2>\n\nCrie um arquivo, Functions3.py, implementando as seguintes fun&ccedil;&otilde;es com respectivas derivadas\n      <OL TYPE=a>\n        <LI>\n$f_{1}(x)=x^2+x-6, &#92;quad  f_1&#92;prime(x)= 2x+1                  &#92;quad x_0=1.5;$\n        </LI>\n        <LI>\n$f_{2}(x)=x^3-9x+3,        &#92;quad  f_2&#92;prime(x)= 3x^2-9,               &#92;quad x_0=1.5;$\n        </LI>\n        <LI>\n$f_{3}(x)=x^2-2,           &#92;quad  f_3&#92;prime(x)= 2x,                   &#92;quad x_0=1.5.$\n        </LI>\n     </OL>\nCrie um executavel, Run.Newton_Raphson.py, executando o algoritmo Newton Raphson, conforme indicado acima.\n\n<P>\nRepita a execu&ccedil;&atilde;o acima com mais 5 fun&ccedil;&otilde;es.\n\n@Exec 01.py', '2', 155, 1, '1', '1', '1', '2', '2', '', '', '/usr/local/Slides/1_Disciplines/1_CN/1_Functions/0_Zeros/4_Newton_Raphson/99_Activities', '1', '99_Activities', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
