(301, 1689343937, 1689342938, 1689343937, 'Determinant Revisited', 'Determinant', 'As $&#92;underline{&#92;widehat r}&#039;(t)=v(t) &#92;underline{n}(t)$:\r\n&#92;[\r\n &#92;underline{r}&#039;&#039;(t) &#92;cdot &#92;underline{n}(t)\r\n =\r\n &#92;frac{1}{v(t)} &#92;underline{r}&#039;&#039;(t) &#92;cdot &#92;underline{&#92;widehat r}&#039;(t)\r\n =\r\n &#92;frac{d(t)}{v(t)}\r\n &#92;]', '', 270, 1, '1', '', '7', '2', '1', '', '', '', '2', '8', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(302, 1691506499, 1689343890, 1691506499, 'Angular Velocity', 'Angular Velocity', 'Thus, he unknown function, $&#92;omega(t)$, appearing in the Frenet Equations, has been found:\r\n&#92;[\r\n &#92;omega(t)=&#92;frac{d(t)}{v(t)^2}\r\n&#92;]\r\nReciprocal, where $d(t) &#92;neq 0$:\r\n&#92;[\r\n   &#92;nu(t)\r\n   =\r\n   &#92;frac{1}{&#92;omega(t)}\r\n   =\r\n   &#92;frac{v(t)^2}{d(t)}\r\n&#92;]', '1', 270, 1, '1', '', '7', '2', '', '', '', '', '2', '9', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
